# Bundled TinyExpression catalog (default)
# format:
#   exact|name|description|context(optional)
#   prefixWithSuffix|prefix|_|1|description|context(optional)
tinyexpression-catalog-v1

exact|input|default input value|COMMON
exact|inputName|default name input|COMMON
exact|didCheck|flag set by external checks|COMMON

prefixWithSuffix|nim|_|1|NIM context variable (nim_<suffix>)|NIM
prefixWithSuffix|fa|_|1|FA context variable (fa_<suffix>)|FA
